Text.val: continue with prog if access is not locked, otherwise print message and term

ExpSyntax.val: Trim(OSEnvGet('TEMP')) & '\MSG' & Str({0,1}, '2P0Z0') & '_' & Trim(Str({0,12},'')) & '_' & Trim(Str({0,13},'')) & '_' & DStr(Date(),'YYYYMMDD') & '_' & TStr(Time(),'HHMMSS') & '.csv'

RqHTTPHeader ('Content-type: text/csv','Content-Disposition: attachment; filename='&'MSG' & Str({0,1}, '2P0Z0') & '_' & Trim(Str({0,12},'')) & '_' & Trim(Str({0,13},'')) & '_' & DStr(Date(),'YYYYMMDD') & '_' & TStr(Time(),'HHMMSS') & '.csv')

SQL_STMT_U.val: select IMQD_IMQH_TYPE, COUNT(*) AS N from :1/CFLC c INNER JOIN :1/IMQD m ON m.IMQD_IMQH_ADMNO=c.CFLC_ADMNOALLOWED and m.IMQD_IMQH_CLNTNO=c.CFLC_CLNTNOALLOWED where CFLC_ADMNO=:2 and CFLC_CLNTNO=:3 and CFLC_USRID=':4' and IMQD_DATEANSWER IS NULL :5 GROUP by IMQD_IMQH_TYPE

select m.* from :1/CFLC c INNER JOIN :1/IMQD m ON m.IMQD_IMQH_ADMNO=c.CFLC_ADMNOALLOWED and m.IMQD_IMQH_CLNTNO=c.CFLC_CLNTNOALLOWED where CFLC_ADMNO=:2 and CFLC_CLNTNO=:3 and CFLC_USRID=':4' and IMQD_DATEANSWER IS NULL :5 :6
